<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color:#444;">You’ve Been Invited to Our Ordering Platform</h1>
    
    <p>
      We’re pleased to inform you that you have been invited to join our ordering platform.  
      This account will allow you to manage and place your orders with us directly.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Your login credentials are as follows:
    </p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %><br/>
      <strong>Password:</strong> <%= @password %>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Please sign in using the following link:  
      <a href="<%= new_user_session_url %>" style="color:#1a73e8; text-decoration:none;">Access the Platform</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after your first login.  
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Should you have any questions or require assistance, feel free to contact our support team at any time.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Best regards,<br/>
      <strong>The Shirtpop Team</strong>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
